---
// Phase 6 Task 5-1: HomeIsland.astro
// 기존 apps/web/public/tabs/tab-home.html 컨텐츠를 Astro component 으로 inline.
// tab-loader.js 의 fetch lazy-load 대신 빌드 시 inline → 콘솔 에러 0 + race 제거.
// 기존 initHomeTab() 함수는 app.js 에서 그대로 호출 (tab 진입 시).
// HTML 본문은 tab-home.html 에서 1:1 복사. 수정 금지.
---
<div class="tab-content" id="tab-home">
  <!-- 프로필 미저장 힌트 배너 -->
  <div id="homeProfileNudge" class="info-note-banner hidden">
    <span>📌</span>
    <span>아직 개인정보가 없어요 — <a onclick="switchTab('profile')">직종·호봉</a>을 입력하면 시간외 수당이 자동 계산됩니다.</span>
  </div>

  <!-- 내 현황 요약 카드 -->
  <div class="home-summary-grid">
    <div class="home-summary-card">
      <img src="/overtime.png" alt="시간외" class="home-card-img home-card-img-toggle" id="homeOtImg"
        onclick="switchHomePeriod(_homePeriod === 'month' ? 'year' : 'month')">
      <div class="home-card-body hidden" id="homeOtBody">
        <div class="home-card-stats" id="homeOtStats"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="home-summary-card">
      <img src="/vacation.png" alt="휴가" class="home-card-img home-card-img-toggle" id="homeLeaveImg"
        onclick="switchHomePeriod(_homePeriod === 'month' ? 'year' : 'month')">
      <div class="home-card-body hidden" id="homeLeaveBody">
        <div class="home-card-stats" id="homeLeaveStats"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 사용자 한마디 -->
  <div class="card home-testimonial-card">
    <div class="card-title text-brand-body-large mb-2">
      <span class="icon text-brand-accent-violet">💬</span> 사용자 한마디
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial-slider">
      <div class="testimonial-track">
        <div class="testimonial-item">
          <span class="testimonial-quote">"휴가 얼마나 남았는지 금방 알 수 있어서 휴가계획 짜기 좋아요"</span>
          <span class="testimonial-author">핵의학과 · 보건직</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-item">
          <span class="testimonial-quote">"이번달 온콜 몇 번 했는지 까먹었는데 이제 바로 기록할 수 있어서 최고!"</span>
          <span class="testimonial-author">영상의학과 · 보건직</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-item">
          <span class="testimonial-quote">"연차 남은 거 휴대폰에서 바로 알 수 있어서 좋아요"</span>
          <span class="testimonial-author">원무과 · 사무직</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-item">
          <span class="testimonial-quote">"이제야 내 통상임금이 어떻게 계산하는지 알겠네요 ㅎㅎ"</span>
          <span class="testimonial-author">영상의학과 · 보건직</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-item">
          <span class="testimonial-quote">"야근했는데 기록이 없어서 수당 빠진 적 있거든요. 이제 미리 확인해요"</span>
          <span class="testimonial-author">진단검사의학과 · 보건직</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-item">
          <span class="testimonial-quote">"내 시간외 근무 수당을 바로 알 수 있어서 좋아요 ㅋㅋ"</span>
          <span class="testimonial-author">외래 간호사 · 3교대</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 공지사항 및 업데이트 -->
  <div class="card home-newsboard">
    <div class="newsboard-tabs">
      <button class="newsboard-tab" data-newstab="notice" onclick="switchNewsTab('notice')">📢 공지사항</button>
      <button class="newsboard-tab active" data-newstab="changelog" onclick="switchNewsTab('changelog')">🎉
        업데이트</button>
    </div>
    <div class="newsboard-body border-t-ds-status-success-25">
      <!-- 공지사항 패널 -->
      <div class="newsboard-panel" id="newsNoticePanel">
        <div class="changelog-pager-content" id="noticeContent"></div>
        <div class="changelog-pager-nav hidden" id="noticeNav">
          <button class="changelog-nav-btn" onclick="noticePage(-1)">‹</button>
          <span class="changelog-pager-indicator" id="noticeIndicator"></span>
          <button class="changelog-nav-btn" onclick="noticePage(1)">›</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 업데이트 패널 -->
      <div class="newsboard-panel active" id="newsChangelogPanel">
        <div class="changelog-pager-content" id="changelogContent"></div>
        <div class="changelog-pager-nav">
          <button class="changelog-nav-btn" id="changelogPrev" onclick="changelogPage(-1)">‹</button>
          <span class="changelog-pager-indicator" id="changelogIndicator"></span>
          <button class="changelog-nav-btn" id="changelogNext" onclick="changelogPage(1)">›</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 프라이버시 안내 -->
  <div class="home-privacy-banner">
    <span>🔐</span>
    <span>모든 데이터는 내 브라우저에만 저장됩니다.<br> 개발자도, 서버도 절대 볼 수 없어요.</span>
  </div>

  <!-- ── Desktop right-context panel (≥1280px only — desktop-shell.css) ── -->
  <aside class="tab-desktop-context" aria-label="홈 컨텍스트">
    <div class="ds-ctx-section">실시간 컨텍스트 · 홈</div>
    <div class="ds-ctx-card" id="homeCtxProfile">
      <div class="ds-ctx-title">👤 프로필 완성도 <small id="homeCtxProfilePct">—</small></div>
      <div class="ds-ring-wrap">
        <div class="ds-ring">
          <svg width="52" height="52"><circle cx="26" cy="26" r="22" fill="none" stroke="#e5e7eb" stroke-width="6"></circle><circle id="homeCtxRing" cx="26" cy="26" r="22" fill="none" stroke="#6C5CE7" stroke-width="6" stroke-dasharray="0 138" stroke-linecap="round"></circle></svg>
          <div class="ds-ring-pct" id="homeCtxRingPct">—</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="ds-ctx-muted" id="homeCtxMissing">완료까지 — 항목</div>
          <a class="ds-ctx-link-xs" onclick="if(window.switchTab)switchTab('profile')">→ 채우기</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ds-ctx-card">
      <div class="ds-ctx-title">⏰ 이번 주 시간외 <small id="homeCtxOtPct">—</small></div>
      <div class="home-progress-wrap ds-ctx-progress-compact"><div class="home-progress-bar ds-ctx-progress-amber" id="homeCtxOtBar"></div></div>
      <div class="ds-ctx-row ds-ctx-row-spaced"><span class="k">누적</span><span class="v" id="homeCtxOtSum">— h</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="ds-ctx-card">
      <div class="ds-ctx-title">📢 최신 공지</div>
      <div id="homeCtxNotices" class="ds-ctx-note">불러오는 중…</div>
    </div>
    <div class="ds-ctx-card">
      <div class="ds-ctx-title">⚡ 빠른 액션</div>
      <div class="ds-ctx-row ds-ctx-action" onclick="if(window.switchTab)switchTab('payroll')"><span class="k">📤</span><span class="v">명세서 업로드</span></div>
      <div class="ds-ctx-row ds-ctx-action" onclick="if(window.switchTab)switchTab('overtime')"><span class="k">⏱️</span><span class="v">시간외 입력</span></div>
      <div class="ds-ctx-row ds-ctx-action" onclick="if(window.switchTab)switchTab('reference')"><span class="k">📖</span><span class="v">규정 검색</span></div>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <!-- 홈 대시보드 스타일 (KPI / 차트 / 액션 / 커리어) -->
  <style is:global>
    .home-dashboard { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }

    /* 모바일 — KPI strip 5칸 → 2 col + 마지막 full */
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; }
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi > :nth-child(5) { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border-active);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md, 12px);
      padding: 10px 12px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 600; }
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi-value { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text-primary); margin-top: 2px; font-family: 'Space Grotesk','Inter',sans-serif; line-height: 1.1; }
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi-trend { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 600; margin-top: 4px; }
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi.indigo { background: var(--accent-indigo); }
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi.cyan { background: var(--accent-cyan); }
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi.amber { background: var(--accent-amber); }
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi.emerald { background: var(--accent-emerald); }
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi.indigo .ds-kpi-label,
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi.indigo .ds-kpi-value,
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi.indigo .ds-kpi-trend,
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi.emerald .ds-kpi-label,
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi.emerald .ds-kpi-value,
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi.emerald .ds-kpi-trend { color: white; }
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi.indigo .ds-kpi-label,
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi.indigo .ds-kpi-trend,
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi.emerald .ds-kpi-label,
    .home-dashboard .dash-kpi .ds-kpi.emerald .ds-kpi-trend { opacity: 0.85; }

    /* 차트 row */
    .home-dashboard .dash-charts { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 12px; }
    .home-dashboard .dash-meta {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-top: 6px;
      padding-top: 6px;
      border-top: 1px dashed var(--border-glass);
    }
    .home-dashboard .dash-empty {
      padding: 16px 8px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      background: var(--bg-elevated, rgba(0,0,0,0.02));
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .home-dashboard .dash-donut-row {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; padding: 4px 0;
    }
    .home-dashboard .dash-donut-legend {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px;
      font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    .home-dashboard .dash-donut-legend strong { color: var(--text-primary); margin-left: 4px; }
    .home-dashboard .dash-dot { display: inline-block; width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 6px; vertical-align: middle; }

    /* 다음 액션 */
    .home-dashboard .dash-actions { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
    .home-dashboard .dash-action {
      display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: var(--bg-card);
      transition: background 0.15s;
    }
    .home-dashboard .dash-action[data-action-tab]:hover { background: var(--bg-glass-hover, rgba(0,0,0,0.04)); }
    .home-dashboard .dash-action.amber { border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-amber); }
    .home-dashboard .dash-action.rose { border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-rose); }
    .home-dashboard .dash-action.emerald { border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-emerald); }
    .home-dashboard .dash-action-icon { font-size: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .home-dashboard .dash-action-label { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); }
    .home-dashboard .dash-action-desc { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2px; }

    /* 커리어 타임라인 */
    .home-dashboard .dash-career { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 10px; }
    .home-dashboard .dash-career-item {
      padding: 10px;
      background: var(--bg-elevated, rgba(0,0,0,0.02));
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .home-dashboard .dash-career-label { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .home-dashboard .dash-career-value { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text-primary); margin-top: 4px; font-family: 'Space Grotesk','Inter',sans-serif; }
    .home-dashboard .dash-career-meta { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2px; }

    /* 데스크탑 — KPI 5 col / 차트 2 col */
    @media (min-width: 769px) {
      .home-dashboard .dash-kpi { grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); }
      .home-dashboard .dash-kpi > :nth-child(5) { grid-column: auto; }
      .home-dashboard .dash-charts { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</div>
